#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.197"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.197:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.197:0.2"
msgid "20. Mahāvagga "
msgstr "20. The Great Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: mallikāsuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.197:0.3"
msgid "197. Mallikādevīsutta "
msgstr "197. Queen Mallikā "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.197:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "

msgctxt "an4.197:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho mallikā devī yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnā kho mallikā devī bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Queen Mallikā went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.203, sc2
msgctxt "an4.197:2.1"
msgid "“Ko nu kho, bhante, hetu ko paccayo, yena midhekacco mātugāmo dubbaṇṇā ca hoti durūpā supāpikā dassanāya; "
msgstr "“What is the cause, sir, what is the reason why in this life some females are ugly, unattractive, and bad-looking; "

msgctxt "an4.197:2.2"
msgid "daliddā ca hoti appassakā appabhogā appesakkhā ca? "
msgstr "and poor, with few assets and possessions; and insignificant? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.197:3.1"
msgid "Ko pana, bhante, hetu ko paccayo, yena midhekacco mātugāmo dubbaṇṇā ca hoti durūpā supāpikā dassanāya; "
msgstr "And why are some females ugly, unattractive, and bad-looking; "

msgctxt "an4.197:3.2"
msgid "aḍḍhā ca hoti mahaddhanā mahābhogā mahesakkhā ca? "
msgstr "but rich, affluent, wealthy, and illustrious? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an4.197:4.1"
msgid "Ko nu kho, bhante, hetu ko paccayo, yena midhekacco mātugāmo abhirūpā ca hoti dassanīyā pāsādikā paramāya vaṇṇapokkharatāya samannāgatā; "
msgstr "And why are some females attractive, good-looking, lovely, of surpassing beauty; "

msgctxt "an4.197:4.2"
msgid "daliddā ca hoti appassakā appabhogā appesakkhā ca? "
msgstr "but poor, with few assets and possessions; and insignificant? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an4.197:5.1"
msgid "Ko pana, bhante, hetu ko paccayo, yena midhekacco mātugāmo abhirūpā ca hoti dassanīyā pāsādikā paramāya vaṇṇapokkharatāya samannāgatā, aḍḍhā ca hoti mahaddhanā mahābhogā mahesakkhā cā”ti? "
msgstr "And why are some females attractive, good-looking, lovely, of surpassing beauty; and rich, affluent, wealthy, and illustrious?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an4.197:6.1"
msgid "“Idha, mallike, ekacco mātugāmo kodhanā hoti upāyāsabahulā. "
msgstr "“Take a female who is irritable and bad-tempered. "

msgctxt "an4.197:6.2"
msgid "Appampi vuttā samānā abhisajjati kuppati byāpajjati patitthīyati, kopañca dosañca appaccayañca pātukaroti. "
msgstr "Even when criticized a little bit she loses her temper, becoming annoyed, hostile, and hard-hearted, and displaying annoyance, hate, and bitterness. "

#. VAR: Sā → so (s1-3)
msgctxt "an4.197:6.3"
msgid "Sā na dātā hoti samaṇassa vā brāhmaṇassa vā annaṃ pānaṃ vatthaṃ yānaṃ mālāgandhavilepanaṃ seyyāvasathapadīpeyyaṃ. "
msgstr "She doesn’t give to ascetics or brahmins such things as food, drink, clothing, vehicles; garlands, fragrance, and makeup; and bed, house, and lighting. "

#. VAR: Issāmanikā → issāmanako (s1-3) | issamānikā (pts1)
msgctxt "an4.197:6.4"
msgid "Issāmanikā kho pana hoti; "
msgstr "And she’s jealous, "

msgctxt "an4.197:6.5"
msgid "paralābhasakkāragarukāramānanavandanapūjanāsu issati upadussati issaṃ bandhati. "
msgstr "envying, resenting, and begrudging the possessions, honor, respect, reverence, homage, and veneration given to others. "

#. VAR: Sā → so (s1-3)
#. VAR: sā → so (s1-3)
msgctxt "an4.197:6.6"
msgid "Sā ce tato cutā itthattaṃ āgacchati, sā yattha yattha paccājāyati dubbaṇṇā ca hoti durūpā supāpikā dassanāya; "
msgstr "If she comes back to this state of existence after passing away, wherever she is reborn she’s ugly, unattractive, and bad-looking; "

msgctxt "an4.197:6.7"
msgid "daliddā ca hoti appassakā appabhogā appesakkhā ca. "
msgstr "and poor, with few assets and possessions; and insignificant. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.204, sc7
msgctxt "an4.197:7.1"
msgid "Idha pana, mallike, ekacco mātugāmo kodhanā hoti upāyāsabahulā. "
msgstr "Take another female who is irritable and bad-tempered. … "

msgctxt "an4.197:7.2"
msgid "Appampi vuttā samānā abhisajjati kuppati byāpajjati patitthīyati, kopañca dosañca appaccayañca pātukaroti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.197:7.3"
msgid "Sā dātā hoti samaṇassa vā brāhmaṇassa vā annaṃ pānaṃ vatthaṃ yānaṃ mālāgandhavilepanaṃ seyyāvasathapadīpeyyaṃ. "
msgstr "But she does give to ascetics or brahmins … "

msgctxt "an4.197:7.4"
msgid "Anissāmanikā kho pana hoti; "
msgstr "And she’s not jealous … "

msgctxt "an4.197:7.5"
msgid "paralābhasakkāragarukāramānanavandanapūjanāsu na issati na upadussati na issaṃ bandhati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.197:7.6"
msgid "Sā ce tato cutā itthattaṃ āgacchati, sā yattha yattha paccājāyati dubbaṇṇā ca hoti durūpā supāpikā dassanāya; "
msgstr "If she comes back to this state of existence after passing away, wherever she is reborn she’s ugly, unattractive, and bad-looking; "

msgctxt "an4.197:7.7"
msgid "aḍḍhā ca hoti mahaddhanā mahābhogā mahesakkhā ca. "
msgstr "but rich, affluent, wealthy, and illustrious. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "an4.197:8.1"
msgid "Idha pana, mallike, ekacco mātugāmo akkodhanā hoti anupāyāsabahulā. "
msgstr "Take another female who isn’t irritable and bad-tempered. … "

msgctxt "an4.197:8.2"
msgid "Bahumpi vuttā samānā nābhisajjati na kuppati na byāpajjati na patitthīyati, na kopañca dosañca appaccayañca pātukaroti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.197:8.3"
msgid "Sā na dātā hoti samaṇassa vā brāhmaṇassa vā annaṃ pānaṃ vatthaṃ yānaṃ mālāgandhavilepanaṃ seyyāvasathapadīpeyyaṃ. "
msgstr "But she doesn’t give to ascetics or brahmins … "

msgctxt "an4.197:8.4"
msgid "Issāmanikā kho pana hoti; "
msgstr "And she’s jealous … "

msgctxt "an4.197:8.5"
msgid "paralābhasakkāragarukāramānanavandanapūjanāsu issati upadussati issaṃ bandhati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.197:8.6"
msgid "Sā ce tato cutā itthattaṃ āgacchati, sā yattha yattha paccājāyati abhirūpā ca hoti dassanīyā pāsādikā paramāya vaṇṇapokkharatāya samannāgatā; "
msgstr "If she comes back to this state of existence after passing away, wherever she is reborn she’s attractive, good-looking, lovely, of surpassing beauty; "

msgctxt "an4.197:8.7"
msgid "daliddā ca hoti appassakā appabhogā appesakkhā ca. "
msgstr "but poor, with few assets and possessions; and insignificant. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "an4.197:9.1"
msgid "Idha pana, mallike, ekacco mātugāmo akkodhanā hoti anupāyāsabahulā. "
msgstr "Take another female who isn’t irritable and bad-tempered. … "

msgctxt "an4.197:9.2"
msgid "Bahumpi vuttā samānā nābhisajjati na kuppati na byāpajjati na patitthīyati, na kopañca dosañca appaccayañca pātukaroti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.197:9.3"
msgid "Sā dātā hoti samaṇassa vā brāhmaṇassa vā annaṃ pānaṃ vatthaṃ yānaṃ mālāgandhavilepanaṃ seyyāvasathapadīpeyyaṃ. "
msgstr "She gives to ascetics and brahmins … "

msgctxt "an4.197:9.4"
msgid "Anissāmanikā kho pana hoti; "
msgstr "And she’s not jealous … "

msgctxt "an4.197:9.5"
msgid "paralābhasakkāragarukāramānanavandanapūjanāsu na issati na upadussati na issaṃ bandhati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.197:9.6"
msgid "Sā ce tato cutā itthattaṃ āgacchati, sā yattha yattha paccājāyati abhirūpā ca hoti dassanīyā pāsādikā paramāya vaṇṇapokkharatāya samannāgatā; "
msgstr "If she comes back to this state of existence after passing away, wherever she is reborn she’s attractive, good-looking, lovely, of surpassing beauty; "

msgctxt "an4.197:9.7"
msgid "aḍḍhā ca hoti mahaddhanā mahābhogā mahesakkhā ca. "
msgstr "and rich, affluent, wealthy, and illustrious. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "an4.197:10.1"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, mallike, hetu ayaṃ paccayo, yena midhekacco mātugāmo dubbaṇṇā ca hoti durūpā supāpikā dassanāya; "
msgstr "This is why are some females are ugly … "

msgctxt "an4.197:10.2"
msgid "daliddā ca hoti appassakā appabhogā appesakkhā ca. "
msgstr "and poor … and insignificant. "

msgctxt "an4.197:10.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ pana, mallike, hetu ayaṃ paccayo, yena midhekacco mātugāmo dubbaṇṇā ca hoti durūpā supāpikā dassanāya; "
msgstr "And some females are ugly … "

msgctxt "an4.197:10.4"
msgid "aḍḍhā ca hoti mahaddhanā mahābhogā mahesakkhā ca. "
msgstr "but rich … and illustrious. "

msgctxt "an4.197:10.5"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, mallike, hetu ayaṃ paccayo, yena midhekacco mātugāmo abhirūpā ca hoti dassanīyā pāsādikā paramāya vaṇṇapokkharatāya samannāgatā; "
msgstr "And some females are attractive … "

msgctxt "an4.197:10.6"
msgid "daliddā ca hoti appassakā appabhogā appesakkhā ca. "
msgstr "but poor … and insignificant. "

msgctxt "an4.197:10.7"
msgid "Ayaṃ pana, mallike, hetu ayaṃ paccayo, yena midhekacco mātugāmo abhirūpā ca hoti dassanīyā pāsādikā paramāya vaṇṇapokkharatāya samannāgatā; "
msgstr "And some females are attractive … "

msgctxt "an4.197:10.8"
msgid "aḍḍhā ca hoti mahaddhanā mahābhogā mahesakkhā cā”ti. "
msgstr "and rich … and illustrious.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.205, sc11
msgctxt "an4.197:11.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, mallikā devī bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When this was said, Queen Mallikā said to the Buddha: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: nūnāhaṃ → sā nūnāhaṃ (s1-3) | yaṃ nūnāhaṃ (pts1, mr)
#. VAR: aññaṃ jātiṃ → aññāya jātiyā (s1-3)
msgctxt "an4.197:11.2"
msgid "“yā nūnāhaṃ, bhante, aññaṃ jātiṃ kodhanā ahosiṃ upāyāsabahulā, "
msgstr "“Sir, in another life I must have been irritable and bad-tempered. "

msgctxt "an4.197:11.3"
msgid "appampi vuttā samānā abhisajjiṃ kuppiṃ byāpajjiṃ patitthīyiṃ kopañca dosañca appaccayañca pātvākāsiṃ, "
msgstr "Even when lightly criticized I must have lost my temper, becoming annoyed, hostile, and hard-hearted, and displaying annoyance, hate, and bitterness. "

msgctxt "an4.197:11.4"
msgid "sāhaṃ, bhante, etarahi dubbaṇṇā durūpā supāpikā dassanāya. "
msgstr "For now I am ugly, unattractive, and bad-looking. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc12
#. VAR: aḍḍhā → aḍḍhā ca (bj, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an4.197:12.1"
msgid "Yā nūnāhaṃ, bhante, aññaṃ jātiṃ dātā ahosiṃ samaṇassa vā brāhmaṇassa vā annaṃ pānaṃ vatthaṃ yānaṃ mālāgandhavilepanaṃ seyyāvasathapadīpeyyaṃ, sāhaṃ, bhante, etarahi aḍḍhā mahaddhanā mahābhogā. "
msgstr "In another life I must have given to ascetics or brahmins such things as food, drink, clothing, vehicles; garlands, fragrance, and makeup; and bed, house, and lighting. For now I am rich, affluent, and wealthy. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc13
msgctxt "an4.197:13.1"
msgid "Yā nūnāhaṃ, bhante, aññaṃ jātiṃ anissāmanikā ahosiṃ, paralābhasakkāragarukāramānanavandanapūjanāsu na issiṃ na upadussiṃ na issaṃ bandhiṃ, sāhaṃ, bhante, etarahi mahesakkhā. "
msgstr "In another life, I must not have been jealous, envying, resenting, and begrudging the possessions, honor, respect, reverence, homage, and veneration given to others. For now I am illustrious. "

msgctxt "an4.197:13.2"
msgid "Santi kho pana, bhante, imasmiṃ rājakule khattiyakaññāpi brāhmaṇakaññāpi gahapatikaññāpi, tāsāhaṃ issarādhipaccaṃ kāremi. "
msgstr "In this royal court I command maidens of the aristocrats, brahmins, and householders. "

msgctxt "an4.197:13.3"
msgid "Esāhaṃ, bhante, ajjatagge akkodhanā bhavissāmi anupāyāsabahulā, "
msgstr "So, sir, from this day forth I will not be irritable and bad-tempered. "

msgctxt "an4.197:13.4"
msgid "bahumpi vuttā samānā nābhisajjissāmi na kuppissāmi na byāpajjissāmi na patitthīyissāmi, kopañca dosañca appaccayañca na pātukarissāmi; "
msgstr "Even when heavily criticized I won’t lose my temper, become annoyed, hostile, and hard-hearted, or display annoyance, hate, and bitterness. "

msgctxt "an4.197:13.5"
msgid "dassāmi samaṇassa vā brāhmaṇassa vā annaṃ pānaṃ vatthaṃ yānaṃ mālāgandhavilepanaṃ seyyāvasathapadīpeyyaṃ. "
msgstr "I will give to ascetics or brahmins such things as food, drink, clothing, vehicles; garlands, fragrance, and makeup; and bed, house, and lighting. "

msgctxt "an4.197:13.6"
msgid "Anissāmanikā bhavissāmi, paralābhasakkāragarukāramānanavandanapūjanāsu na ississāmi na upadussissāmi na issaṃ bandhissāmi. "
msgstr "I will not be jealous, envying, resenting, and begrudging the possessions, honor, respect, reverence, homage, and veneration given to others. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.197:13.7"
msgid "Abhikkantaṃ, bhante … pe … upāsikaṃ maṃ, bhante, bhagavā dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti. "
msgstr "Excellent, sir! … From this day forth, may the Buddha remember me as a lay follower who has gone for refuge for life.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.197:13.8"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

